# Changelog

## [0.3.2] - 2026-05-06

### Added
- handling multiple frequency id values in FITS-IDI file.
- `python-casacore` dependency for handling table I/O operations.
- configurations `mpi_cores_importfitsidi` 

### Changed
- `AvicaAverageMs` runs iteratively for each `MS` file using `mpicasa` from user provided `casadir`.
- `ImportFitsIdi` parallelized using `mpicasa` from user provided `casadir`.

### Fixed
- python environment collisions with `casadir`
- issue of `binary` data in FITS-IDI table columns.
- counting multiple frequency ID values in FREQUENCY FITS-IDI table.

### Removed
- `casatools` from internal dependencies.

[0.3.2]: https://github.com/avikhagol/avica/compare/v0.2.0...v0.3.2
[0.3.1] : https://github.com/avikhagol/avica/compare/v0.1.2...v0.3.1
